* work in progress *


* INSTALL
    $ https://github.com/jackdoe/roar
    $ cd roar && make

* USAGE
    $ ./roar ./echo.sh /directory-you-want-to-watch

    it will execute ./echo.sh with arguments:
        echo.sh ACTION OBJ_TYPE FILE for example:
    DELETE FILE /tmp/xyz
    MOVE FILE /tmp/xyz /tmp/xyy
    MODIFY DIRECTORY /tmp/yxz

    MODIFY includes create, attr change, but not MOVE
